### MoodMix — Auth (passwordless email code)
@base = http://localhost:8000
@email = {{$dotenv CONTACT_TO_EMAIL}}


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Sign-in flow (visual test for the email)
#
# 1. Run "Request a sign-in code" — Resend delivers the email to {{email}}.
# 2. Open the inbox and tweak the HTML/CSS in
#    backend/app/services/auth_service.py (_build_html_body) until happy.
# 3. Paste the 6-digit code into the verify-code request below and run it.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Request a sign-in code (sends the email)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/request-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}"
}

### Verify the code (paste the 6 digits you received in `code`)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/verify-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "code": ""
}
